      • setAnalyticFunctionOrdering

        public void setAnalyticFunctionOrdering(boolean analyticFunctionOrdering)
        Set whether we want to use an analytic function ordering, in the case that we use heuristic evaluation of condensation sets. This may give worse results than the alternative ordering method, but will not take unreasonable amounts of time on diffiult rules. It is enabled by default when using heuristics.
